headline: Goldman Sachs Is Positive on Republic Services (RSG)
summary: Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE:RSG) is one of the best industrial stocks to buy. On November 24, Goldman Sachs assigned a Buy rating on RSG, with an accompanying price target of $255.
